<br>
Hold this stone anywhere in your inventory and wait until the &quot;Mystic Voice&quot; counts down the port timer to one minute.  There will be a nice &quot;large ring&quot; effect then everyone in the circle will be ported up to the Nexus in Luclin.  The wait is never more than 15 minutes.<br>
<br>
Mobs in the Nexus, Bazaar, and probably Shadow Haven are also non-factioned, to an extent.  If you are not liked there, they will not attack you, but will simply not sell to you (and probably cuss you out).<br>
